Ornaments are items with exceptionally high <link=\"DECOR\">Decor</link>, and must be displayed on a <link=\"ITEMPEDESTAL\">Pedestal</link> or <link=\"SHELF\">Display Shelf</link> in order to be counted toward a room's requirements.\n\nThey can be obtained through exploration, excavation, and study. Some are admired in their original form, while others can be reworked or crafted by <link=\"ARTING1\">creative</link> Duplicants.